# Project Standards

## Browser Compatibility
- All code must work in the **latest stable versions** of Chrome, Firefox, and Safari.
- No vendor-prefixed CSS or non-standard JS APIs without a cross-browser fallback.
- Test SVG, CSS transitions/animations, and JS features against all three engines.

## Versioning
- At the **start of a new working session** (first edit of the session), copy the current `index.html` to `previous_iterations/index-vN.html` (increment N from the highest existing version).
- Do **not** create a new version copy for subsequent edits within the same session.
- The root `index.html` always holds the latest version.
- Never delete previous iterations.
